  "title": "Hiring Coordinator (Temp) | Immediate Start!",
  "description": "<p>Join <strong>Octomate Staffing</strong>, where tech boosts meets talent. Work with a vibrant team that’s reshaping how candidates and companies find the right match! 🚀</p>\n<p>📍<strong>:</strong> Orchard<br>\n 🕗<strong>:</strong> 8:30am – 5:30pm<br>\n 📅<strong>:</strong> Monday – Friday<br>\n 📆<strong>:</strong> Immediate – 3 months (extendable / convertible!)<br>\n 💸<strong>:</strong> $12/hour</p>\n<p>💼 <strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Post and manage job ads with optimised visibility</li>\n  <li>Source, screen, and shortlist awesome candidates</li>\n  <li>Work with different stakeholders on interviews, offers, and onboarding</li>\n  <li>Keep our candidate database neat and up to date</li>\n</ul>\n<p>✅ <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Confident and upbeat communicator</li>\n  <li>Organised and hungry to learn in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Able to commit for minimally 3 months</li>\n  <li>Completed GCE A-Level/ Diploma/ Degree holders are welcome</li>\n</ul>",
